Come on, L. Let's turn up!

18:03.416 --> 18:05.585
Just ignore him.

18:05.618 --> 18:07.587
Are you seeing any other colors?

18:07.620 --> 18:08.921
* But they's counterfeit...

18:08.955 --> 18:10.257
Come on, turn it off.

18:10.290 --> 18:11.991
Turn it off!

18:12.024 --> 18:13.993
-* From the last young brother
that they... * -(music stops)

18:16.296 --> 18:18.665
It's just anger with no purpose.

18:18.698 --> 18:21.501
Keep working on it, Shine,
and do better.

18:24.371 --> 18:26.606
I know what I'm doing, okay? I'm
going to get one of my people.

18:26.639 --> 18:29.842
Okay, Lucious, why don't you
work with Veronica, huh?

18:29.876 --> 18:30.910
You seem to be comfortable
with that.

18:30.943 --> 18:32.111
I-If I can just have

18:32.145 --> 18:33.313
a little bit of time
alone with him,

18:33.346 --> 18:34.747
I think I could really help.

18:34.781 --> 18:36.916
I-I know what
I need to do, okay?

18:36.949 --> 18:39.152
Uh, Lucious, you can't just...

18:39.186 --> 18:40.987
CLAUDIA: Okay, I said
I would stick close.

18:41.020 --> 18:43.256
I'm gonna bring him back.

18:43.290 --> 18:45.091
Uh, that's-that's-that's
off the record.

18:45.124 --> 18:46.693
Yeah, off the record. Delete.

18:46.726 --> 18:48.661
You heard him. He's bringing in
one of his O.G.s.

18:48.695 --> 18:49.896
Go get coffee, take a break.

18:52.699 --> 18:54.201
-ANDRE: Yeah, I say
we send them home. -COOKIE: No.

18:54.234 --> 18:55.535
Claudia promised
she would bring him back.

18:55.568 --> 18:57.103
Just give them
a couple of minutes.

18:57.136 --> 18:59.138
-All right? Patience.
-Look, I don't like

18:59.172 --> 19:01.708
to be the bearer of bad news,
but the board is saying that...

19:01.741 --> 19:03.543
Look, I don't give a damn
what the board says.

19:06.413 --> 19:08.448
-Okay, what is the board saying?
-(chuckles)

19:08.481 --> 19:10.517
If the album doesn't drop
as scheduled,

19:10.550 --> 19:12.151
and Empire takes another hit
in the press...

19:13.486 --> 19:14.687
...they're gonna ask you
to step down.

19:16.723 --> 19:18.325
Damn.

19:18.358 --> 19:21.361
Oh, if Lucious was here,
he could finesse those fools,

19:21.394 --> 19:24.697
and lace them tracks if he could
remember a damn thing.

19:27.667 --> 19:29.502
Okay, go ahead, send them home.

19:31.371 --> 19:34.307
-THIRSTY: That's the best you
can do at this point... -Just...

19:34.341 --> 19:36.008
-REPORTER: Hey, guys, look.
-(gasps)

19:36.042 --> 19:37.710
REPORTER 2:
Is that Eddie Barker?

19:37.744 --> 19:40.680
-I'm-a go check on Hakeem
and the lawyer. -Okay. Bye.

19:40.713 --> 19:41.848
REPORTER 2:
That's Eddie Barker.

19:41.881 --> 19:43.049
-Hey.
-COOKIE: Eddie.

19:43.082 --> 19:44.050
Hey.

19:44.083 --> 19:46.018
Hey.
(laughing): Hey.

19:46.052 --> 19:47.587
-Lucious told me we were going
to make some music. -Yes!

19:47.620 --> 19:49.389
I pushed off
my trip to Barbados.

19:49.422 --> 19:52.024
-Thank you. -And then meet me
in the conference room.

19:52.058 --> 19:53.192
He may not remember this place,

19:53.226 --> 19:54.761
but he knows
you care about it, so...

19:54.794 --> 19:56.863
LUCIOUS: I told y'all
I was bringing an O.G.

19:56.896 --> 19:59.031
See? I told you.

19:59.065 --> 20:00.600
I told you Lucious
was pulling together

20:00.633 --> 20:02.669
some of the most
incredible producers

20:02.702 --> 20:04.003
to finish this album.

20:04.036 --> 20:05.905
And only he could get
Eddie Barker

20:05.938 --> 20:07.507
back in the booth.

20:07.540 --> 20:09.676
I told Lu that I might need him
to nudge me a little bit

20:09.709 --> 20:10.710
'cause it's been a while
since I've been

20:10.743 --> 20:11.944
-back in the studio.
-(laughter)

20:11.978 --> 20:13.680
(quietly):
I love you so much for this.

20:13.713 --> 20:14.881
I love you, too. Come on.

20:14.914 --> 20:16.048
Let's go make some music.

20:16.082 --> 20:18.851
(overlapping chatter)

20:18.885 --> 20:20.620
COOKIE:
Tiana, baby.

20:20.653 --> 20:21.954
I would like for you
to meet Eddie Barker.

20:21.988 --> 20:24.023
He's gonna produce
your track with Lucious.

20:24.056 --> 20:27.694
Yo, Lucious Lyon
and Eddie Barker?

20:27.727 --> 20:30.129
All right, now, sit your ass
down, babe. That's enough.

20:30.162 --> 20:32.299
-Wow. -EDDIE: I love
your stuff, Tiana.

20:32.332 --> 20:34.033
I'm honored to be
working with you.

20:34.066 --> 20:35.935
Oh, my God. Um, seriously.

20:35.968 --> 20:37.370
Y-You're a legend.

20:37.404 --> 20:38.938
No, sweetheart, tonight,
it's all about

20:38.971 --> 20:40.640
this legend right here.

20:40.673 --> 20:42.309
What's the megahit
that we're gonna be remixing

20:42.342 --> 20:44.577
for this lovely, amazing woman?

20:44.611 --> 20:46.813
Um, actually,
Lucious is insistent

20:46.846 --> 20:49.582
on having Tiana and Hakeem
do "Hate the Game"

20:49.616 --> 20:50.783
from Paid in Cash, right?

20:50.817 --> 20:53.219
COOKIE:
Great, so where's Hakeem?

20:53.252 --> 20:55.154
Um, he needs a minute.

20:55.187 --> 20:56.823
He had, like, 136, though,

20:56.856 --> 20:59.158
so what's the problem?

20:59.191 --> 21:01.928
Uh, how about we hear your part
while we wait for Hakeem?

21:01.961 --> 21:03.162
You okay with that, Lu?

21:03.195 --> 21:04.764
Yeah, I mean, if you're good,
I'm good.

21:05.932 --> 21:07.166
-Jump in the booth?
-Cool.

21:07.199 --> 21:08.968
-(chuckles)
-(beat starts playing)

21:19.779 --> 21:23.616
* When you out here in the cold,
you can't trust a soul *

21:23.650 --> 21:26.453
* Got to play your cards,
you can never fold *

21:26.486 --> 21:29.622
* If you call yourself a man,
you got to hold your ground *

21:29.656 --> 21:33.660
* Make a plan and don't let
nobody hold you down... *

21:33.693 --> 21:35.962
Quiet as it's kept, this, uh,

21:35.995 --> 21:38.130
is one of Cookie's favorites.

21:38.164 --> 21:39.699
Ain't that right, Cook?

21:39.732 --> 21:41.834
Don't do that.
Don't do that.

21:41.868 --> 21:43.603
* That gon' getcha killed...

21:43.636 --> 21:45.872
Look, don't be modest.

21:45.905 --> 21:48.508
Look, you've shared so much
with these fine people.

21:48.541 --> 21:51.978
Why not share
why this is your favorite?

21:52.011 --> 21:54.347
Well, because y'all always like
to give Lucious all the credit.

21:54.381 --> 21:55.815
I guess 'cause he's a man.

21:55.848 --> 21:57.517
But I pimped this bitch.
All of it.

21:57.550 --> 22:00.219
(laughter)

22:00.252 --> 22:02.188
* Because a pimp
gon' be a pimp *

22:02.221 --> 22:06.659
* A player gonna play the game

